[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Anyone able to successfully sell the message card jewelry on Tiktokshop by creating videos - and linking it to a product in make this an automated process by doing the following. 1) Create the products in Shineon (Special Orders/Partner (CSV/API) [and keeping track of the SKUs] 2) Manually add the product to Tiktok Shop (with the SKU that's in your Shineon products) 3) Every time someone makes purchase through your Tiktok Shop, you will get an email 4) Use N8N (a workflow agent) that will trigger everytime an order email comes from the Tiktok Shop 5) Use that email to extract the user's info, product ID/SKU they order, etc. Format it to a CSV. 6) Use Shineon API /v1/orders endpoint to send the order to ShineOn ! Adding the products will be manual but the fulfilment process can all be automated through the Tiktok Shop and Shineon. No need for Shopify, Facebook ads, Tiktok Ads. Just focus on creating great videos organically on Tiktok and link the product to your tiktok shop. Let me know if this possible with Shineon I'll research this automated TikTok Shop + ShineOn fulfillment process for you. Let me gather the latest information on both platforms' capabilities and create a comprehensive implementation guide. Using Tool | Search ShineOn print on demand API v1/orders endpoint documentation 2024 View Using Tool | Search TikTok Shop seller email notifications order automation workflow View Using Tool | Search N8N workflow automation TikTok Shop order processing tutorial View Using Tool | Search ShineOn CSV upload partner orders special orders feature View Let me get more specific information about ShineOn's API documentation and TikTok Shop's notification system. Using Tool | Read https://teamshineon.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/10120654767121-The-ShineOn-API View Using Tool | Read https://teamshineon.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/10121370441873-CSV-Ordering View Using Tool | Search TikTok Shop order notification email format 